<![CDATA[<p class="p1" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999">Hi {!Account.FirstName},</font></p><p class="p2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p class="p1" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999">How did your orientation go? Did all of your questions and concerns get addressed? I hope everything went great for you and you are ready to love your new boat. Was there anything else that we could have done differently to serve you better?</font></p><p class="p1" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p class="p1" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999">Please keep in mind that if you are ever in need of assistance with your boating that I am always around to help as best as I can, with a great team here at Legend Boats to help serve you as well. Do not hesitate if you have any other questions or concerns and I would love to help.</font></p><p class="p2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p class="p1" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999">Thank you from all of us at Legend Boats. &nbsp;I hope to see you again very soon.</font></p><p class="p2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p class="p1" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999">Best Regards,</font></p><p class="p2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p class="p2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#999999"><br></font></p><p class="p3" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font color="#999999"><span class="s1">{!User.Name}</span><span class="s2">&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="p3" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2" color="#999999"><span class="s1">{!User.Title}</span><span class="s2">&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="p4" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 1